797
00:32:46.959 --> 00:32:50.559
Sentado a cierta distancia, bostezaba con aire importante.

798
00:32:51.839 --> 00:32:52.480
Evidentemente,

799
00:32:52.959 --> 00:32:53.839
Marméladov

800
00:32:53.839 --> 00:32:56.240
