892
00:36:25.284 --> 00:36:25.605
Sea,

893
00:36:26.560 --> 00:36:27.760
exeomo.

894
00:36:28.720 --> 00:36:32.320
Permítame, joven, que le pregunte si puede usted

895
00:36:32.320 --> 00:36:33.040
o,

896
00:36:33.280 --> 00:36:34.400
