14319
09:13:36.707 --> 09:13:39.187
Sí, es un buen hombre, un hombre de

14320
09:13:39.187 --> 09:13:39.907
mérito,

14321
09:13:39.987 --> 09:13:40.787
instruido,

14322
09:13:40.867 --> 09:13:41.907
inteligente,

14323
09:13:42.547 --> 09:13:43.666
dijo Rascónicov,

14324
09:13:43.666 --> 09:13:46.067
