14381
09:15:47.562 --> 09:15:48.682
palabras de la joven.

14382
09:15:49.402 --> 09:15:50.121
Después,

14383
09:15:50.202 --> 09:15:51.562
con aire melancólico,

14384
09:15:51.562 --> 09:15:52.361
